put-stderr}\n\n```\nWarning in lsoda(y, times, func, parms, lags = control, ...): Excessive\nprecision requested.  scale up `rtol' and `atol' e.g by the factor 10\n```\n\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr}\n\n```\nWarning in lsoda(y, times, func, parms, lags = control, ...): Returning early.\nResults are accurate, as far as they go\n```\n\n\n:::\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\n# --- 4. 绘图 (修正 Z 轴范围) ---\nI_mat <- out[, (N+2):(2*N+1)]\n\nplot_ly(z = ~I_mat, x = ~x, y = out[,1], type = \"surface\") %>%\n  layout(\n    title = \"Fig 7: I(x,t) Inhomogeneous Steady-state\",\n    scene = list(\n      xaxis = list(title = \"x\",range = c(0, 4)),\n      yaxis = list(title = \"t\",range = c(0, 400)),\n      zaxis = list(title = \"I(x,t)\", range = c(1, 2)) # 修改此处：包含 1.56\n    )\n  )\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"plotly html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-8ad065e01e29987b13c1\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-8ad065e01e29987b13c1\">{\"x\":{\"visdat\":{\"4e2c52743192\":[\"function () \",\"plotlyVisDat\"]},\"cur_data\":\"4e2c52743192\",\"attrs\":{\"4e2c52743192\":{\"z\":{},\"x\":{},\"y\":[0,2,4,6,8,10,12,14,16,16.726204023523405],\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"type\":\"surface\"}},\"layout\":{\"margin\":{\"b\":40,\"l\":60,\"t\":25,\"r\":10},\"title\":\"Fig 7: I(x,t) Inhomogeneous Steady-state\",\"scene\":{\"xaxis\":{\"title\":\"x\",\"range\":[0,4]},\"yaxis\":{\"title\":\"t\",\"range\":[0,400]},\"zaxis\":{\"title\":\"I(x,t)\",\"range\":[1,2]}},\"hovermode\":\"closest\",\"showlegend\":false,\"legend\":{\"yanchor\":\"top\",\"y\":0.5}},\"source\":\"A\",\"config\":{\"modeBarButtonsToAdd\":[\"hoverclosest\",\"hovercompare\"],\"showSendToCloud\":false},\"data\":[{\"colorbar\":{\"title\":\"I_mat\",\"ticklen\":2,\"len\":0.5,\"lenmode\":\"fraction\",\"y\":1,\"yanchor\":\"top\"},\"colorscale\":[[\"0\",\"rgba(68,1,84,1)\"],[\"0.0416666666666667\",\"rgba